            "title": "日股曾跌近1170點　半日跌666點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">日股跌幅收窄至不足700點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">日經指數早段曾跌至53286點，跌近1170點，半日收報53786點，跌666點，跌幅1.22%。</p>\n</div>",
